These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, orchid, sunflower, poppy, balloon-flower, iris
1. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsdaffodil##2
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |    4    |   5    |    6     |    7     |
| Flower   | sunflower | iris | daisy | balloon-flower | orchid | poppy | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, mystery, musical, drama, comedy, sports, adventure
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2     |   3    |    4     |    5    |  6   |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | superhero | sports | mystery | drama | musical | adventure |

