.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, brazilian, polish, nigerian, mexican, french, egyptian
1. the polish is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the italian is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
5. the nigerian is on the left of the italian##1
6. the italian is on the left of the mexican##1
7. the polish is in an even position##4
8. the italian is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |      3      |         4          |      5       |     6     |    7    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | nigerian | italian | mexican | egyptian | polish | french |

