.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, thriller, sports, time-travel, epic, crime
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
3. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | crime | sports | epic | time-travel | thriller | satire |

