3. the lawyer is on the right of the electrician##1
4. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
5. the engineer is on the left or right of the pilot##3
6. the bartender is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
