3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
6. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
7. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
8. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Food   | cherry | blueberry | strawberry | pineapple | lettuce | eggplant | corn |

