.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, cat, hamster, rat, lizard, goat
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the hamster is the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the lizard##2
6. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Pet   | snake | hamster | rat | lizard | goat | cat | goldfish |

