4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |     3     |   4    |    5    |  6  |  7   |
| Birthday   | june | october | february | may | july | january | march |

