.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, november, march, december, may, august, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Birthday   | november | july | january | december | may | march | august |

 